track_notes:
easy and short trail from Col Joux. 
Near autobahn exit Chatillon . After the trek you can enjoy a thermal bath or sauna in StVincent.
First part of trail in the wood, second part more sleep and often iced, last part on the ridge with beautiful views on both side of Valle d Aosta.
Summit is large and NOT rocky so you can pick any kind of antenna.  BUT SOTA-Etiquette !!! Leave place for other trekkers
track_title: Class Easy short  but North path in winter is iced you need crampons

track_notes: easy access from col de joux. wonderful views on Aosta valleys.
